Congratulations on your big win tonight!

554
00:43:55,423 --> 00:43:56,922
Thanks, man.

555
00:43:56,924 --> 00:43:59,326
You went in as the underdog in a lot
of people's minds. What happened?

556
00:43:59,328 --> 00:44:03,363
