00:44:29,657 --> 00:44:30,591
Felt pretty good.

565
00:44:32,126 --> 00:44:35,963
- Oh my God, your eye!
- Looks worse than it is.

566
00:44:41,302 --> 00:44:42,403
You take that.

567
00:44:44,171 --> 00:44:44,939
Come on.

568
00:44:46,207 --> 00:44:48,042
