looking out for you.

693
00:56:52,030 --> 00:56:53,631
Is that what you're doing?

694
00:56:55,967 --> 00:56:58,033
[announcer] <i>And now for the moment
you've all been waiting for.</i>

695
00:56:58,035 --> 00:56:59,835
